alk, Persuasion, Lying, etc) while atop the pile.', 'Crossed'=>'Target takes -1 Success Levels on any Charm offensive (Fast Talk, Persuasion, Lying, etc) while atop the pile.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Plan', 'Normal'=>'+1 Success Level when working with others while atop pile.', 'Crossed'=>'+1 Success Level when working alone while atop pile.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Mage', 'Normal'=>'+1 Success Level to all Magic Annexes and Tests to do with Magic, wisdom and intellect while atop the pile.', 'Crossed'=>'-1 Success Level to all Magic Annexes and Tests to do with Magic, wisdom and intellect while atop the pile.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Death', 'Normal'=>'While atop the Target&#39;s pile all Wounds created by the Target are +1 Level and unaffected by Passive Defences (Unsoakable).', 'Crossed'=>'Cancels a Crisis.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Crisis', 'Normal'=>'The good becomes bad and vice versa for the player. Automatic Proficiency Crisis.', 'Crossed'=>'Cancels a Proficiency Crisis.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Jam / Parry / Dodge', 'Normal'=>'Ignore an attack as it is Jammed, Parried or Dodged Autromatically', 'Crossed'=>'Cancels a Successful Dodge or Parry'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Fast Talk', 'Normal'=>'Automatic Success on any Charm attempt', 'Crossed'=>'Automatic Failure of any Charm attempt'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Surprise', 'Normal'=>'Target may act immediately, ignoring RT, GRT and Ordeal Pool Size', 'Crossed'=>'Target is immediately affected by GRT of 1'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Stalemate', 'Normal'=>'Target may automatically Stalemate any Test (Scoring exactly the Difficulty)', 'Crossed'=>'Cancels a Stalemate or Draw with a random Success Level up or down.'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Failure', 'Normal'=>'Target rolls a Complete Failure or Draws minimum.', 'Crossed'=>'+2 Success Levels to one roll, or Ordeal Card'),array('Wyrd_Tarot'=>'Psst', 'Normal'=>'Add a card from your Hand to the Target&#39;s Hand and Draw 2 cards.', 'Crossed'=>'Take a random card from the Target&#39;s Hand and add 