array('Type'=>'Quantum', 'Description'=>'We all make choices that seperate who we are from who we might have been. Quantum Alternates see beyond those choices. They communicate across Dimensions and show how they might have turned out different. They are classic <q>What if...?</q> Questions answered.')));
