array('Type'=>'Locked','Description'=>'The way is blocked by a Locked Door, Gate, or Portal. Sometimes you can pick the lock, or find a key, sometimes you just have to break through.'), //ace
array('Type'=>'Stuck','Description'=>'The way is blocked by something that is stuck. It could be a door, a car across the road, or a plank wedged in the way. You&#39;ll have to give it a shove or find tools.'),  //2
array('Type'=>'Hidden','Description'=>'The way is hidden, or secret, you might have to hunt around or get lucky to find the way.'), //3
array('Type'=>'Maze','Description'=>'The way is blocked, but by a Maze, Labyrinth, Ropewalk or something that confuses the route you should take. You need a way to find the path.'), //4
array('Type'=>'Barricade','Description'=>'The way is blocked, deliberately, it could be traffic works or furniture stacked against the door. Barricades are sometimes hastily assembled and may have a weakpoint, but you&#39;ll need to find it and get through.'), //5
array('Type'=>'Gauntlet','Description'=>'The way is blocked, but by Characters. Maybe they&39;re a tight crowd cuing outside a shop, or a phalanx of the Royal Guard, choose carefully or there may be a fight.'), //6
array('Type'=>'Guardian Beast','Description'=>'The way ahead is blocked, perhaps by a fierce dog, a bull elephant, or even a chained sewer dragon. '), //7
array('Type'=>'Steam Vent','Description'=>'The way is blocked, by fog, smoke or steam, it may be coming from underground, or out of a building, or pipe. It might be deadly, or just obscuring.'), //9
array('Type'=>'Flood','Description'=>'The way is blocked by water. It might be a flash flood, a swollen river, a flooded passage, or just a huge puddle, but you will have to get wet to move on.'),//9
array('Type'=>'Dead-End','Description'=>'This way is blocked, completely. Perhaps the roof collapsed, or maybe it was just always a dead-end. You have gone the wrong way, and have to double back. It might mean there was a hidden way you missed.'), //10
array('Type'=>'Choice','Description'=>'A difficult choice. You may draw two more cards to represent the choice here. Each way has a different Obstacle.'), //J
array('Type'=>'Puzzle','Description'=>'The way is blocked by soe sort of Puzzle. It could be a combination lock, or a series of clues that must be solved, or a particular setting of levers or a computer that must be hacked...'), //Q
array('Type'=>'Guarded','Description'=>'The way ahead is Guarded, there is probably a Gatehouse, and a security Guard, or perhaps a Security Desk. You might be able to sneak, or fast-talk your way past, or this will become a fight.'), //K
//hearts
array('Type'=>'Handicap','Description'=>'The Obstacle will trigger a Handicap. E.g. If Arachnophobia is the Handicap then there is a spider in the way.'), //ace
array('Type'=>'Dilemma','Description'=>'The Obstacle is an Ethical or Moral Dilemma. E.g. You witness a robbery, but see the robber immediately give the money to a charity. What will you say when the Police ask?'),  //2
array('Type'=>'Shopping','Description'=>'You need to make a purchase, or several purchases, before you can move ahead. Characters have to make it through the tedium, and not get sidetracked, or spend too much money.'), //3
array('Type'=>'Nightmare','Description'=>'Bad dreams can stop us from being at our best. Nightmares can stop us from functioning if they come often enough.'), //4
array('Type'=>'Fake-out','Description'=>'Sometimes an obvious trap isn&#39;t a trap at all, or is an old trap that has been disarmed.'), //5
array('Type'=>'Yuk','Description'=>'To proceed you&#39;ll have to do something disgusting, like drinking/swimming through sewage, spoiled milk, vomit, you know something really gross.'), //6
array('Type'=>'Contest','Description'=>'To move on you&#39;ll first have to compete in a contest (and often win). It could be a drinking or eating contest, a test of strength, or skill, or an old-fashioned riddle contest.'), //7
array('Type'=>'Prank','Description'=>'The Obstacle is a (mostly) harmless prank. A bucket of water over a door, or a bannaskin under a rug are examples.'), //9
array('Type'=>'Temptation','Description'=>'The Obstacle is a temptation, traditionally this is represented by a Pleasure Dome filled with loads of semi-naked women.'),//9
array('Type'=>'Proof','Description'=>'A test of honour, the Character must prove their worth, usually by keeping their word or prooving their fealty.'), //10
array('Type'=>'Lie','Description'=>'The Obstacle requires you to Lie for all you&#39;re worth and pretend to be something you are not. It might be that the way ahead is only allowed for someone of a particualr rank, gender or race, and you have to bluff your way ahead.'), //J
array('Type'=>'Anima','Description'=>'The Character is stopped by meeting a personifciation (or extreme example) of their feminine side.'), //Q
array('Type'=>'Animus','Description'=>'The Character is stopped by meeting a personification (or extreme example) of their Masculine side.'), //K
//clubs
array('Type'=>'Chasm','Description'=>'There is a gap, crack, hole, trench, or moat that blocks the way ahead.'), //ace
array('Type'=>'Slick','Description'=>'The way ahead is slippery.'),  //2
array('Type'=>'Sticky','Description'=>'The way ahead is sticky or muddy making the going difficult.'), //3
array('Type'=>'Temperature','Description'=>'The way ahead is baking hot or freezing cold.'), //4
array('Type'=>'Bad-Air','Description'=>'The way ahead may just smell bad, or the air may be unbreathable.'), //5
array('Type'=>'Rapids','Description'=>'The way ahead may be blocked by a river, or the river ahead by rapids.'), //6
array('Type'=>'Unstable','Description'=>'The ground ahead is unstable, it might be loose rocks, scree, rubble, or fallen logs, who knows.'), //7
array('Type'=>'Low-Visibility','Description'=>'The way ahead is dark, smoky, hazy, or brilliantly lit, either way you can&#39;t see much.'), //9
array('Type'=>'Ledge','Description'=>'That chasm, river or lava field ahead, there is one way past, that narrow bridge or ledge. Keep your balance and you&#39;ll be fine.'),//9
array('Type'=>'Squeeze','Description'=>'There is a way ahead, but it is very narrow. Perhaps the road ahead is narrowed by parked cars, tight walls, or low ceilings.'), //10
array('Type'=>'Climb','Description'=>'It might be a steep hill, a cliff, a flight of stairs or a ladder, but you are going to have to go up (or down) it.'), //J
array('Type'=>'Weather','Description'=>'It seems the Weather is not on your side and is hampering your progress, winds are against you, rain, hail, snow, even the sun, whatever really. The Weather is a (Chorus) Extra.'), //Q
array('Type'=>'Disaster','Description'=>'It might be a fire, flood, earthquake or something more uncommon, but every now and then the planet tries to kill us. This is just such an example, a (Force of Nature) Extra.'), //K
