		$this->addHandicap('Hesitant (Specify)','Those with the Hesitant Handicap are not quick to judge, or actually do much of anything. They may be indecisive, or just slow, perhaps they finally get there, perhaps not.',21, 1, 6, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Humble (Specify)','Some Characters have humble beginnings, and some Descendants are always Humble. It might be low-powered, a non-fully featured trial-version or just a cheaper model.',21, 1, 7, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Worthy (Specify)','A Descendant with the Worthy Handicap may only be used, or perhaps owned by those the Handicap specifies. This might be a particular class, type, or race of person, or a specified individual. Alternately perhaps the Worthy Handicap just makes the Descendant more desired, amongst a certain group.',21, 1, 8, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Hallowed (Specify)','The Descendant with a Hallowed Handicap is revered, kept safe, hidden away, or usually enshrined somewhere. The Catholic Church wouldn\'t want you turning the Shroud of Turin into a battle standard, for example.',21, 1, 9, true,true,10,1);
		//Wyrd
