		$this->addHandicap('Dreams (Specify)','Sometimes a Character seems fine in their day-to-day life, but a Doomed Handicap can affect their sleep instead. Perhaps they dream of another life, in another world, or their dreams come true, or perhaps they have only nightmares when they rest.',22, 1, 5, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Haunted (Specify)','A Character with a Haunted Handicap might be haunted by memories of their youth, the choices they once made, a lost love (although that could be a Lament instead). Or they may actually have to go toe-to-toe, or have a heart-to-heart with a ghost or poltergeist.',22, 1, 6, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Prophecy (Specify)','The Prophecy Handicap is useful for slapping on Characters and Descendants that fulfull some grand plan decided by deities, demons or solos. They might be named in a specific Prophecy, or believe a Prophecy is about them. They may even be a prophet themselves, creating future Chronoliths that may come to pass.',22, 1, 7, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Weird (Specify)','Sometimes a Doomed Handicap just makes something Weird. Weird Handicaps are suitable for odd devices and contraptions, dream descendants and anything truly strange or inexplicable.',22, 1, 8, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Paradoxical (Specify)','The Paradoxical Handicap is for things that don\'t make a lot of sense. they might be created by a Temporal paradox, or just be nonsensical, or Oxymoronic.' ,22, 1, 9, true,true,10,1);
