		$this->addHandicap('Affected Sense (Specify)','Sometimes the Loss of Sense Handicap actually refers to some sense that is out of whack rather than missing. A Character might be always hungry or have a twisted sense of morals with this Handicap.',23, 1, 5, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Loss of Sense (Specify)','Sometimes the only way to describe a Loss of a Sense is as exactly that, even though the cause may be social. A Character might be Oblivious, or suffer from Hysterical Blindness, or be an Incurable Romantic.',23, 1, 6, true,true,10,1);
		$this->addHandicap('Insensible (Specify)','Insensible Handicaps are for Characters and Descendants that just seem to have lost touch with reality a little. An example includes how all problems look flammable to a wizard with a fireball spell, or if you only have a hammer all problems look like nails...',23, 1, 7, true,true,10,1);
